<component type="desktop-application">
	<id>io.github.jazztickets.irrlamb</id>
	<name>irrlamb</name>
	<summary>3D physics game in which you control a blue ball of energy in an attempt to touch all glowing orbs</summary>
	<description>
		<p>Find all the orbs in this challenging 3D physics game, using either mouse/keyboard or gamepad.</p>
		<p>35 levels, including 15 tutorials, 7 "campaign" levels, 4 skateparks, 7 challenges, and 2 secrets.</p>
		<p>Keep track of your fastest times and save replays.</p>
	</description>
